title: Torrent
description:
Hello, TPB!

This is my first torrent, so I'd really appreciate it if some people seed.

This torrent contains a copy of "Kingdom Hearts" for the PS2 in .iso format. The torrent also contains the emulator PCSX2, which is needed to run the game. I included the emulator for Windows, Mac OS X, and Linux. The version of the emulator is 1.0.0 for Windows/Linux and 0.9.7 for Mac OS X. Enjoy!

~5chris100
